        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-226",
        "content": "An hour after she had read it, she was driving down the long straight road to Cairo; embarked at Alexandria the next day; landed at Brindisi, and this night and day travelling had brought her at last within sight of the shores of England.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
