        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-226",
        "content": "That she was going to him, Jane knew; but she felt utterly unable to arrange how or in what way her going could be managed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
