        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-226",
        "content": "That it was a complicated problem, her common sense told her; though her yearning arms and aching bosom cried out: \"O God, is it not simple?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
