        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-226",
        "content": "\"Seven pence 'apenny of this stuff ain't much for carrying all that along, I DON'T think!\" grumbled his mate; and Jane's young porter experienced the double joy of faith confirmed, and willing service generously rewarded.",
