        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-226",
        "content": "The young porter, who still stood sentry at the door of Jane's compartment, dashed off to the refreshment room; and, just as the train began to move, handed a cup of steaming coffee and a plate of bread and butter in at the window.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
